 However, the undesirable effects of aromatherapy were mostly only in the irritated skin 

00:04:02.529 --> 00:04:05.750
 when applying essential oils to the skin, 

00:04:05.754 --> 00:04:08.630
 or worse, as a result of their swallowing. 

00:04:08.634 --> 00:04:13.510
 Some citrus oils can make our skin sensitive to the sun. 

00:04:13.513 --> 00:04:16.900
 This is obviously not such a big deal in France 

